gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 112, Bucks 108
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets defeated the Bucks, 112-108. Alperen Sengun recorded 21 points, 11 rebounds, and four assists for the Rockets, with Jalen Green adding 16 points and four rebounds in the victory. Giannis Antetokounmpo tallied 48 points and 17 rebounds for the Bucks in the losing effort. The Rockets improve to 18-16 in the regular season, while the Bucks fall to 25-11.
